    {
      "id": "start_001",
      "type": "start",
      "position": { "x": 100, "y": 50 },
      "data": { "label": "开始测试", "title": "奉天证道：大唐20人格测试", "background": "/assets/background.jpg" }
    },
    {
      "id": "scene_001",
      "type": "scene",
      "position": { "x": 0, "y": 200 },
      "data": {
        "label": "Q1 陨星初坠",
        "dialogue": "长安地陷，大唐国运崩裂。衍天宗密使告知你四地遭袭，而此刻废墟中传来微弱呼救，远方烽烟已起。面对这开局的混乱，你的第一反应是：",
        "speaker": "系统",
        "interactionType": "tap",
        "choices": [
          { "id": "q1_opt1", "text": "A. 协助密使稳住阵脚，优先确认受灾情报与卷轴安全", "vector": { "x": 2, "y": 0, "z": 0 }, "dropFragmentId": null },
          { "id": "q1_opt2", "text": "B. 闭目调息，在天地巨变中守住灵台清明，不因乱象动摇", "vector": { "x": -5, "y": 0, "z": 0 }, "dropFragmentId": null },
          { "id": "q1_opt3", "text": "C. 哪还顾得上那么多！冲进废墟深处，誓要救出每一个被埋的人", "vector": { "x": 5, "y": 0, "z": 0 }, "dropFragmentId": "frag_scroll" },
          { "id": "q1_opt4", "text": "D. 退至高处观察烽烟走向，试图从乱象中找出幕后黑手的轨迹", "vector": { "x": -2, "y": 0, "z": 0 }, "dropFragmentId": "frag_scroll" }
        ],
        "stageWeight": 1.0,
        "background": "/workspace/bg/G1.png"
      }
    },
    { "id": "calc_001", "type": "calculator", "position": { "x": 0, "y": 500 }, "data": { "label": "计算", "description": "应用 Q1 陨星初坠 向量" } },
    {
      "id": "scene_002",
      "type": "scene",
      "position": { "x": 600, "y": 200 },
      "data": {
        "label": "Q2 乱局传承",
        "dialogue": "武林传承面临断代之危，乱军肆虐，如果只能带走一样东西，你下意识的抉择是：",
        "speaker": "系统",
        "interactionType": "tap",
        "choices": [
          { "id": "q2_opt1", "text": "A. 带走无辜的妇孺，人的生命才是文明存在的意义", "vector": { "x": 0, "y": -2, "z": 0 }, "dropFragmentId": null },
          { "id": "q2_opt2", "text": "B. 哪怕背负万难，也要保全门派典籍与火种，绝不让文明熄灭", "vector": { "x": 0, "y": 5, "z": 0 }, "dropFragmentId": null },
          { "id": "q2_opt3", "text": "C. 趁乱寻得一线生机，带大家隐世避祸，活下去才有未来", "vector": { "x": 0, "y": -5, "z": 0 }, "dropFragmentId": null },
          { "id": "q2_opt4", "text": "D. 优先保全核心机密与布防图，为日后反攻留存资本", "vector": { "x": 0, "y": 2, "z": 0 }, "dropFragmentId": null }
        ],
        "stageWeight": 1.0,
        "background": "/workspace/bg/G2.png"
      }
    },
    { "id": "calc_002", "type": "calculator", "position": { "x": 600, "y": 500 }, "data": { "label": "计算", "description": "应用 Q2 乱局传承 向量" } },
    {
      "id": "scene_003",
      "type": "scene",
      "position": { "x": 1200, "y": 200 },
      "data": {
        "label": "Q3 西行孤影",
        "dialogue": "偶遇莫雨、穆玄英一行人西行追查。看着他们逆行的背影，你决定：",
        "speaker": "系统",
        "interactionType": "tap",
        "choices": [
          { "id": "q3_opt1", "text": "A. 保持冷峻，各自有各自的使命，互不干涉才是乱世常态", "vector": { "x": -5, "y": 0, "z": 0 }, "dropFragmentId": null },
          { "id": "q3_opt2", "text": "B. 上前叫住他们，毫无保留地共享长安情报，叮嘱万加小心", "vector": { "x": 5, "y": 0, "z": 0 }, "dropFragmentId": null },
          { "id": "q3_opt3", "text": "C. 托人送去一壶'浮生醉'，遥敬这段未知的归途", "vector": { "x": 2, "y": 0, "z": 0 }, "dropFragmentId": "frag_wine" },
          { "id": "q3_opt4", "text": "D. 隐于暗处观察片刻，记录下他们的行进路线作为参考", "vector": { "x": -2, "y": 0, "z": 0 }, "dropFragmentId": null }
        ],
        "stageWeight": 1.0,
        "background": "/workspace/bg/G3.png"
      }
    },
    { "id": "calc_003", "type": "calculator", "position": { "x": 1200, "y": 500 }, "data": { "label": "计算", "description": "应用 Q3 西行孤影 向量" } },
    {
      "id": "scene_004",
      "type": "scene",
      "position": { "x": 1800, "y": 200 },
      "data": {
        "label": "Q4 号牌骚乱",
        "dialogue": "万花谷口病患如潮，有人因排队失控试图冲击医者。一边是即将崩溃的秩序，一边是倒地不起的老人，你会：",
        "speaker": "系统",
        "interactionType": "tap",
        "choices": [
          { "id": "q4_opt1", "text": "A. 这种时候管什么排队！直接冲过去先救倒地的老人", "vector": { "x": 0, "y": -5, "z": 0 }, "dropFragmentId": "frag_needle" },
          { "id": "q4_opt2", "text": "B. 协助阿麻吕强行隔离闹事者，必须维护队列，否则谁也救不了", "vector": { "x": 0, "y": 5, "z": 0 }, "dropFragmentId": null },
          { "id": "q4_opt3", "text": "C. 冷眼旁观，在混乱中寻找可能趁乱滋事的异族探子", "vector": { "x": 0, "y": -2, "z": 0 }, "dropFragmentId": null },
          { "id": "q4_opt4", "text": "D. 挡在医者身前制止攻击，并在事后耐心听取家属苦衷", "vector": { "x": 0, "y": 2, "z": 0 }, "dropFragmentId": "frag_needle" }
        ],
        "stageWeight": 1.0,
        "background": "/workspace/bg/G4.png"
      }
    },
    { "id": "calc_004", "type": "calculator", "position": { "x": 1800, "y": 500 }, "data": { "label": "计算", "description": "应用 Q4 号牌骚乱 向量" } },
    {
      "id": "scene_005",
      "type": "scene",
      "position": { "x": 2400, "y": 200 },
      "data": {
        "label": "Q5 药王遗烬",
        "dialogue": "孙思邈圆寂，裴元托付给你一名幼童。面对这个或许是‘最后救赎’的孩子，你对他说的第一句话是：",
        "speaker": "系统",
        "interactionType": "tap",
        "choices": [
          { "id": "q5_opt1", "text": "A. 别怕，我会带你去看一眼谷外未被遮蔽的天空。", "vector": { "x": 0, "y": 0, "z": -5 }, "dropFragmentId": null },
          { "id": "q5_opt2", "text": "B. 跟紧我。这也是任务的一部分。", "vector": { "x": 0, "y": 0, "z": 5 }, "dropFragmentId": "frag_note" },
          { "id": "q5_opt3", "text": "C. 把手给我，我发誓会把你安全带出去。", "vector": { "x": 0, "y": 0, "z": -2 }, "dropFragmentId": null },
          { "id": "q5_opt4", "text": "D. 告诉我你现在的身体感受，我们需要制定最优撤离方案。", "vector": { "x": 0, "y": 0, "z": 2 }, "dropFragmentId": "frag_note" }
        ],
        "stageWeight": 1.0,
        "background": "/workspace/bg/G5.png"
      }
    },
    { "id": "calc_005", "type": "calculator", "position": { "x": 2400, "y": 500 }, "data": { "label": "计算", "description": "应用 Q5 药王遗烬 向量" } },
    {
      "id": "scene_006",
      "type": "scene",
      "position": { "x": 3000, "y": 200 },
      "data": {
        "label": "Q6 三星崩塌",
        "dialogue": "三星望月被炸，苏凤棠在火海中抢救典籍，另一边难民在哭喊。火光映照下，你的抉择是：",
        "speaker": "系统",
        "interactionType": "tap",
        "choices": [
          { "id": "q6_opt1", "text": "A. 优先引导难民撤离，书没了可以再写，人死了无法复生", "vector": { "x": 0, "y": -2, "z": 0 }, "dropFragmentId": null },
          { "id": "q6_opt2", "text": "B. 冲入火海协助抢救典籍，这是文明的根基，不容有失", "vector": { "x": 0, "y": 5, "z": 0 }, "dropFragmentId": "frag_secret" },
          { "id": "q6_opt3", "text": "C. 护紧怀中遗孤，顺着密道离开，绝不偏离原本的使命", "vector": { "x": 0, "y": 2, "z": 0 }, "dropFragmentId": null },
          { "id": "q6_opt4", "text": "D. 逆着人流寻找潜伏的爆破手，必须让他付出代价", "vector": { "x": 0, "y": -5, "z": 0 }, "dropFragmentId": null }
        ],
        "stageWeight": 1.0,
        "background": "/workspace/bg/G6.png"
      }
    },
    { "id": "calc_006", "type": "calculator", "position": { "x": 3000, "y": 500 }, "data": { "label": "计算", "description": "应用 Q6 三星崩塌 向量" } },
    {
      "id": "scene_007",
      "type": "scene",
      "position": { "x": 3600, "y": 200 },
      "data": {
        "label": "Q7 听香坊",
        "dialogue": "高绛婷陷入狂暴，无差别攻击周围。面对这位昔日的琴魔，你决定：",
        "speaker": "系统",
        "interactionType": "tap",
        "choices": [
          { "id": "q7_opt1", "text": "A. 结成剑阵，正面压制！为了大局，必须先让她失去行动能力", "vector": { "x": 0, "y": 0, "z": 5 }, "dropFragmentId": "frag_move" },
          { "id": "q7_opt2", "text": "B. 护住身后的孩子，哪怕受伤也要大声呼喊，试图唤醒她的神智", "vector": { "x": 0, "y": 0, "z": -5 }, "dropFragmentId": null },
          { "id": "q7_opt3", "text": "C. 寻找并灭掉周围的迷香陷阱，从源头上削弱幻境影响", "vector": { "x": 0, "y": 0, "z": 2 }, "dropFragmentId": "frag_move" },
          { "id": "q7_opt4", "text": "D. 擒贼先擒王，直接截杀控制她的水贼头目", "vector": { "x": 0, "y": 0, "z": -2 }, "dropFragmentId": null }
        ],
        "stageWeight": 1.0,
        "background": "/workspace/bg/G7.png"
      }
    },
    { "id": "calc_007", "type": "calculator", "position": { "x": 3600, "y": 500 }, "data": { "label": "计算", "description": "应用 Q7 听香坊 向量" } },
    {
      "id": "scene_008",
      "type": "scene",
      "position": { "x": 4200, "y": 200 },
      "data": {
        "label": "Q8 忆盈楼",
        "dialogue": "唐怀仁布下火雷，木楼将塌。公孙二娘去追敌，燕燕被困。千钧一发之际：",
        "speaker": "系统",
        "interactionType": "tap",
        "choices": [
          { "id": "q8_opt1", "text": "A. 追杀唐怀仁！比起救一人，斩草除根才能永绝后患", "vector": { "x": 0, "y": 0, "z": 5 }, "dropFragmentId": null },
          { "id": "q8_opt2", "text": "B. 护住燕燕和受伤弟子撤往水边，用身体为她们挡住气浪", "vector": { "x": 0, "y": 0, "z": -5 }, "dropFragmentId": "frag_drum" },
          { "id": "q8_opt3", "text": "C. 观察爆炸间隙，冷静计算出一条最优的生路", "vector": { "x": 0, "y": 0, "z": 2 }, "dropFragmentId": "frag_drum" },
          { "id": "q8_opt4", "text": "D. 随二娘冲锋，哪怕只有一线机会也要阻止暗器发动", "vector": { "x": 0, "y": 0, "z": -2 }, "dropFragmentId": null }
        ],
        "stageWeight": 1.0,
        "background": "/workspace/bg/G8.png"
      }
    },
    { "id": "calc_008", "type": "calculator", "position": { "x": 4200, "y": 500 }, "data": { "label": "计算", "description": "应用 Q8 忆盈楼 向量" } },
    {
      "id": "scene_009",
      "type": "scene",
      "position": { "x": 4800, "y": 200 },
      "data": {
        "label": "Q9 秀坊合一",
        "dialogue": "大战方歇，作为见证者，在前往下一个目的地前，你会：",
        "speaker": "系统",
        "interactionType": "tap",
        "choices": [
          { "id": "q9_opt1", "text": "A. 迅速整理情报，马不停蹄动身前往藏剑，那里更需要我", "vector": { "x": 5, "y": 0, "z": 0 }, "dropFragmentId": null },
          { "id": "q9_opt2", "text": "B. 独自去水边祭奠死者，在喧嚣后寻求片刻的孤独与反思", "vector": { "x": -5, "y": 0, "z": 0 }, "dropFragmentId": null },
          { "id": "q9_opt3", "text": "C. 留下来安顿伤员，至少在离开前多做一点是一点", "vector": { "x": 2, "y": 0, "z": 0 }, "dropFragmentId": null },
          { "id": "q9_opt4", "text": "D. 清理残骸，研究火雷阵留下的碎瓷，分析敌人的技术特征", "vector": { "x": -2, "y": 0, "z": 0 }, "dropFragmentId": "frag_porcelain" }
        ],
        "stageWeight": 1.0,
        "background": "/workspace/bg/G9.png"
      }
    },
    { "id": "calc_009", "type": "calculator", "position": { "x": 4800, "y": 500 }, "data": { "label": "计算", "description": "应用 Q9 秀坊合一 向量" } },
    {
      "id": "scene_010",
      "type": "scene",
      "position": { "x": 5400, "y": 200 },
      "data": {
        "label": "Q10 麒麟战殇",
        "dialogue": "叶蒙血战殉庄，临终前命死守后院。此刻海寇攻势疯狂，看着将军的遗体，你咬牙决定：",
        "speaker": "系统",
        "interactionType": "tap",
        "choices": [
          { "id": "q10_opt1", "text": "A. 杀回去！拼死也要夺回叶蒙将军的遗体，不容英雄受辱！", "vector": { "x": 0, "y": -5, "z": 0 }, "dropFragmentId": null },
          { "id": "q10_opt2", "text": "B. 强忍悲痛，死守后院防线，军令如山，不得不从", "vector": { "x": 0, "y": 5, "z": 0 }, "dropFragmentId": "frag_rumor" },
          { "id": "q10_opt3", "text": "C. 追踪暗处指挥的军师踪迹，这笔账要算在源头上", "vector": { "x": 0, "y": -2, "z": 0 }, "dropFragmentId": null },
          { "id": "q10_opt4", "text": "D. 协助转移神兵麒天、麟战，保住传承才是对逝者最大的告慰", "vector": { "x": 0, "y": 2, "z": 0 }, "dropFragmentId": "frag_rumor" }
        ],
        "stageWeight": 1.0,
        "background": "/workspace/bg/G10.png"
      }
    },
    { "id": "calc_010", "type": "calculator", "position": { "x": 5400, "y": 500 }, "data": { "label": "计算", "description": "应用 Q10 麒麟战殇 向量" } },
    {
      "id": "scene_011",
      "type": "scene",
      "position": { "x": 6000, "y": 200 },
      "data": {
        "label": "Q11 武库死战",
        "dialogue": "武库即将失控，叶英重伤谢采。此刻乱兵涌入，年幼的叶麟身陷险境。你会：",
        "speaker": "系统",
        "interactionType": "tap",
        "choices": [
          { "id": "q11_opt1", "text": "A. 毫不犹豫冲向叶麟，用身体替他挡下那致命一刀", "vector": { "x": 0, "y": 0, "z": -5 }, "dropFragmentId": null },
          { "id": "q11_opt2", "text": "B. 冷静记录谢采的功法破绽，这是千载难逢的情报机会", "vector": { "x": 0, "y": 0, "z": 5 }, "dropFragmentId": "frag_sword_intent" },
          { "id": "q11_opt3", "text": "C. 守在叶英身侧，协助他抵御乱兵，稳住局面", "vector": { "x": 0, "y": 0, "z": -2 }, "dropFragmentId": null },
          { "id": "q11_opt4", "text": "D. 优先破坏地鼠门洞口，从根源上截断敌军增援", "vector": { "x": 0, "y": 0, "z": 2 }, "dropFragmentId": "frag_sword_intent" }
        ],
        "stageWeight": 1.0,
        "background": "/workspace/bg/G11.png"
      }
    },
    { "id": "calc_011", "type": "calculator", "position": { "x": 6000, "y": 500 }, "data": { "label": "计算", "description": "应用 Q11 武库死战 向量" } },
    {
      "id": "scene_012",
      "type": "scene",
      "position": { "x": 6600, "y": 200 },
      "data": {
        "label": "Q12 剑冢迷阵",
        "dialogue": "剑冢大门前，需要有人担任最危险的阵眼守卫，抵挡死士破阵。你擦了擦剑上的血：",
        "speaker": "系统",
        "interactionType": "tap",
        "choices": [
          { "id": "q12_opt1", "text": "A. 默默站在最前方，准备在破阵瞬间第一个杀入", "vector": { "x": 5, "y": 0, "z": 0 }, "dropFragmentId": "frag_rumor" },
          { "id": "q12_opt2", "text": "B. 在旁辅助救治伤员，做好后勤支援", "vector": { "x": -2, "y": 0, "z": 0 }, "dropFragmentId": null },
          { "id": "q12_opt3", "text": "C. 询问谢采行踪，试图摸清这整局阴谋的逻辑", "vector": { "x": -5, "y": 0, "z": 0 }, "dropFragmentId": "frag_rumor" },
          { "id": "q12_opt4", "text": "D. 主动担任阵眼守卫，将后背交给伙伴", "vector": { "x": 2, "y": 0, "z": 0 }, "dropFragmentId": null }
        ],
        "stageWeight": 1.0,
        "background": "/workspace/bg/G12.png"
      }
    },
    { "id": "calc_012", "type": "calculator", "position": { "x": 6600, "y": 500 }, "data": { "label": "计算", "description": "应用 Q12 剑冢迷阵 向量" } },
    {
      "id": "scene_013",
      "type": "scene",
      "position": { "x": 7200, "y": 200 },
      "data": {
        "label": "Q13 宝殿对峙",
        "dialogue": "少林被围，澄正拼死送你突围，嘱托你去后山请援。但途中你看到小沙弥被困，你会：",
        "speaker": "系统",
        "interactionType": "tap",
        "choices": [
          { "id": "q13_opt1", "text": "A. 顺路偷出特制药水，即便此刻违规，也要为破局留一手", "vector": { "x": 0, "y": -5, "z": 0 }, "dropFragmentId": "frag_breath_1" },
          { "id": "q13_opt2", "text": "B. 强忍悲愤，严格遵循嘱托直奔后山，大局为重", "vector": { "x": 0, "y": 5, "z": 0 }, "dropFragmentId": null },
          { "id": "q13_opt3", "text": "C. 顺手救下被盘查的康宴别，掩护小沙弥撤离", "vector": { "x": 0, "y": -2, "z": 0 }, "dropFragmentId": null },
          { "id": "q13_opt4", "text": "D. 潜伏观察月泉淮的阵法，推算其回气间隙", "vector": { "x": 0, "y": 2, "z": 0 }, "dropFragmentId": "frag_breath_1" }
        ],
        "stageWeight": 1.0,
        "background": "/workspace/bg/G13.png"
      }
    },
    { "id": "calc_013", "type": "calculator", "position": { "x": 7200, "y": 500 }, "data": { "label": "计算", "description": "应用 Q13 宝殿对峙 向量" } },
    {
      "id": "scene_014",
      "type": "scene",
      "position": { "x": 7800, "y": 200 },
      "data": {
        "label": "Q14 莲池救赎",
        "dialogue": "幻境即将崩塌，清梵陷入癫狂，马十八在摇铃。面对这混乱的局面：",
        "speaker": "系统",
        "interactionType": "tap",
        "choices": [
          { "id": "q14_opt1", "text": "A. 击杀马十八！物理破除眠术，这是最快最有效的方法", "vector": { "x": 0, "y": 0, "z": 5 }, "dropFragmentId": null },
          { "id": "q14_opt2", "text": "B. 诵念神咒，哪怕希望渺茫，也要试图唤回他的神智", "vector": { "x": 0, "y": 0, "z": -5 }, "dropFragmentId": "frag_breath_2" },
          { "id": "q14_opt3", "text": "C. 观察并记录'眠术规律'，寻找破解之道", "vector": { "x": 0, "y": 0, "z": 2 }, "dropFragmentId": null },
          { "id": "q14_opt4", "text": "D. 抱住受惊的小沙弥，用身体挡住乱石，静候支援", "vector": { "x": 0, "y": 0, "z": -2 }, "dropFragmentId": "frag_breath_2" }
        ],
        "stageWeight": 1.0,
        "background": "/workspace/bg/G14.png"
      }
    },
    { "id": "calc_014", "type": "calculator", "position": { "x": 7800, "y": 500 }, "data": { "label": "计算", "description": "应用 Q14 莲池救赎 向量" } },
    {
      "id": "scene_015",
      "type": "scene",
      "position": { "x": 8400, "y": 200 },
      "data": {
        "label": "Q15 最终归宿",
        "dialogue": "护送任务结束，地宫大门缓缓合拢。在这一刻，你最后的动作是：",
        "speaker": "系统",
        "interactionType": "tap",
        "choices": [
          { "id": "q15_opt1", "text": "A. 弃剑转身，孤独离去，这场长达万里的押运终成往事", "vector": { "x": -5, "y": 0, "z": 0 }, "dropFragmentId": null },
          { "id": "q15_opt2", "text": "B. 望向伊丽川方向，心系战局，随时准备奔赴下一个战场", "vector": { "x": 5, "y": 0, "z": 0 }, "dropFragmentId": null },
          { "id": "q15_opt3", "text": "C. 长揖到地，感谢这一路上的侠义温情", "vector": { "x": -2, "y": 0, "z": 0 }, "dropFragmentId": null },
          { "id": "q15_opt4", "text": "D. 仔细检查遗物是否带到，确认因果已了", "vector": { "x": 2, "y": 0, "z": 0 }, "dropFragmentId": null }
        ],
        "stageWeight": 1.0,
        "background": "/workspace/bg/G15.png"
      }
    },
    { "id": "calc_015", "type": "calculator", "position": { "x": 8400, "y": 500 }, "data": { "label": "计算", "description": "应用 Q15 最终归宿 向量" } },
